{
  "id": "cutting-the-leash",
  "title": "Cutting the Leash",
  "description": "A recruit tangled up with an illegal conglomerate wants out -- to sign on with the Guild instead. The conglomerate doesn't let people just walk away from what they're owed.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "type": "start",
      "text": "Word reaches the crew through channels that don't officially exist: someone inside {enemyGroupName} wants out, and wants in with the Guild instead. {enemyGroupName} does not consider that someone else's decision to make.",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-backchannel",
      "type": "seed",
      "seeds": [
        {
          "target": "candidate",
          "params": {
            "seedId": "conglomerate-defector"
          },
          "note": "A voice on an unlisted channel says they're done running product for {enemyGroupName}, and wants to know if the Guild takes people with debts attached."
        }
      ],
      "completionText": "The defector is brought aboard.",
      "position": {
        "x": 300,
        "y": -150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-smuggle",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Meet in the Dark",
        "description": "Get someone to a meeting point without {enemyGroupName} noticing the pattern.",
        "difficulty": "ROUTINE",
        "tags": [
          "infiltration"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 300,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-ledger",
      "type": "seed",
      "seeds": [
        {
          "target": "shop",
          "params": {
            "itemName": "Coded Debt Ledger"
          },
          "note": "A ledger detailing exactly what {enemyGroupName} thinks it owns, quietly for sale to whoever's asking the right questions."
        }
      ],
      "completionText": "The ledger is in hand.",
      "position": {
        "x": 300,
        "y": 150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act1-ledger-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The ledger checks out. Every debt, every leverage point, all itemized in {enemyGroupName}'s own hand.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "give_item",
          "params": {
            "itemName": "Coded Debt Ledger"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 600,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-1",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "Whichever way the recruit surfaces, the shape of the problem is the same: {enemyGroupName} doesn't lose assets. It collects them.",
      "effects": [],
      "position": {
        "x": 900,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-debt",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Settle the Books",
        "description": "{enemyGroupName} claims the recruit owes them. Negotiate the number down to something that isn't a life sentence.",
        "difficulty": "STANDARD",
        "tags": [
          "negotiation"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 1200,
        "y": -225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-blackmail",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Empty the Vault",
        "description": "{enemyGroupName} is holding something over the recruit's head. Get it before they use it.",
        "difficulty": "STANDARD",
        "tags": [
          "heist"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 1200,
        "y": -75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-enforcers",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Send Them Home Empty-Handed",
        "description": "{enemyGroupName} sends a collection crew to bring the recruit back the hard way. Make sure they leave without them.",
        "difficulty": "HARD",
        "tags": [
          "combat"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 1200,
        "y": 75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "act2-papers",
      "type": "seed",
      "seeds": [
        {
          "target": "shop",
          "params": {
            "itemName": "Forged Identity Papers"
          },
          "note": "A forger who owes someone a favor can bury the recruit's old name, for a price."
        }
      ],
      "completionText": "The papers are ready.",
      "position": {
        "x": 1200,
        "y": 225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bridge-2",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "On paper, in ledgers, in whatever passes for memory at {enemyGroupName}, the recruit is starting to look less and less like property.",
      "effects": [],
      "position": {
        "x": 1500,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "endgame-choice",
      "type": "choice",
      "text": "There's no version of this where {enemyGroupName} just says goodbye. How does the recruit actually get free?",
      "choiceOptions": [
        {
          "id": "buyout",
          "label": "Buy out the contract outright"
        },
        {
          "id": "expose",
          "label": "Burn {enemyGroupName}'s operation down in public"
        },
        {
          "id": "vanish",
          "label": "Fake the recruit's death and vanish them"
        },
        {
          "id": "sellout",
          "label": "Sell the recruit back for Guild favor"
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 1800,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-buyout-mission",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Buy the Contract",
        "description": "Money talks louder than loyalty, most places. Make {enemyGroupName} an offer that's easier to take than to refuse.",
        "difficulty": "STANDARD",
        "tags": [
          "negotiation"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": -300
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-buyout-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The paperwork changes hands without ceremony.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_perk",
          "params": {
            "perkName": "Bought Free"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": -375
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-buyout-success-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "success",
      "text": "The paperwork changes hands, and just like that, the recruit belongs to nobody. {enemyGroupName} took the money and didn't blink -- which is its own kind of unsettling.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": -375
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-buyout-fail-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "{enemyGroupName} takes the money and keeps the leash anyway, quietly, for later.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_flaw",
          "params": {
            "flawName": "Marked Debtor"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": -225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-buyout-fail-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "failure",
      "text": "The offer is accepted, the debt is not forgotten. {enemyGroupName} doesn't forget anything.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": -225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-expose-mission",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Burn It Down",
        "description": "With proof in hand, take {enemyGroupName}'s operation apart in public, where it can't be quietly fixed.",
        "difficulty": "HARD",
        "tags": [
          "sabotage"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": -150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-expose-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The ledger goes public, page by page.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "give_item",
          "params": {
            "itemName": "A Conglomerate's Enemies"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "apply_perk",
          "params": {
            "perkName": "Made an Example"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": -75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-expose-success-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "success",
      "text": "{enemyGroupName}'s operation comes apart in the open, ledger and all. The recruit walks away clean, and {enemyGroupName} has bigger fires to put out than one missing asset.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": -75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-expose-fail-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The evidence doesn't hold up once it's in the open.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_flaw",
          "params": {
            "flawName": "Exposed Too Early"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": 75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-expose-fail-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "failure",
      "text": "The story doesn't stick. Now {enemyGroupName} knows exactly who's been digging.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": 75
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-expose-noledger-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "failure",
      "text": "Without proof, going public plays as a wild accusation from a merc crew with an axe to grind. {enemyGroupName} laughs it off, and remembers who said it.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-vanish-mission",
      "type": "mission",
      "mission": {
        "title": "Make Them a Ghost",
        "description": "Faking a death convincingly enough that {enemyGroupName} actually believes it takes more than a body double.",
        "difficulty": "HARD",
        "tags": [
          "extraction"
        ]
      },
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": 150
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-vanish-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The paperwork, the body, the story -- all of it holds together, at least on the surface.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_perk",
          "params": {
            "perkName": "Ghost"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": 225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-vanish-success-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "success",
      "text": "As far as {enemyGroupName}'s records are concerned, the recruit died owing them money -- a satisfying way for the story to end for everyone except {enemyGroupName}.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": 225
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-vanish-fail-payoff",
      "type": "story",
      "text": "The ruse doesn't hold.",
      "effects": [
        {
          "type": "apply_flaw",
          "params": {
            "flawName": "Unconvincing Corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": 375
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-vanish-fail-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "failure",
      "text": "{enemyGroupName} works out fairly quickly that the recruit is worth more walking around, and starts looking.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": 375
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "finale-sellout-end",
      "type": "end",
      "outcome": "failure",
      "text": "The recruit gets walked right back to {enemyGroupName}'s door, and the Guild gets paid for the trouble of not caring. Whatever trust might have grown out of this doesn't.",
      "position": {
        "x": 2100,
        "y": 300
      }
    }
  ],
